Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//===============TEXT===============
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 你也真是喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢海了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也最喜欢奶奶做的猪肉味噌汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从海里出来之后就尽情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你热好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:02:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明从明天就要开始高中生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光那家伙准备什么的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这附近的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近刚搬过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢电动车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我从新家去学校硬塞给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近的学校的话是梦丘高中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就和我家孙女—样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是来练习电动车的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 顺便逛逛这附近看看海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝罐装果汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来看海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好看海才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真广阔啊 大海 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 因为姑娘你还年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时候也会认为手掌心大小的身边事物就是世界的全部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起头看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:07:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你眼前广大而有趣的世界正无限展开着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于那位姑娘来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起大海还要宽广的世界在那里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海里面怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水还很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但相对的 透明度非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪肉味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 要给你拿来着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟呵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪肉味噌汤 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家排好队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 别爰上我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一碗五百日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔喔 热乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪肉味噌汤 猪肉味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光 不快点儿过来就要没有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪肉味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陌生的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陌生的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陌生的人群
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你考了电动车驾照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 我也想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位新同学 集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请过来集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要公布分班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自确认好班级和学号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别弄错鞋箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级二班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—切都是新的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所知的东西完全不存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级二班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋箱确认完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子 是刚才那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下-个潜水地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜水地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哟 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很精致又可爰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是拿到了贵重的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 什么贵重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面只是个学校地图而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是说这是从今天开始要来三年的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未知世界的地图吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未知世界 的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很棒的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且能感受到老师想让新生开心的那份爰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先从储物柜往右
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 正如地图上所示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地在四层
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上楼啊爬上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师想让新生开心的那份爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个积极的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜呀 四层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后沿着这走廊直走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就要到达目的地了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是积极
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说是很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哟 这里就是我们今天的潜水点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哟 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈啊 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 全是用粉笔画的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是老师的爰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的座位确认完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是叫小日向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在我后面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子确认完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椅子确认完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后的一年请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是前后位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也开始上新学校了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道过得还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人分到一个班了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来都坐到自己座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 本班的班主任是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫火鸟真斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后的一年时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长的话三年时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你们应该想了解老师的各种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那些之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先从朋友间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的自我介绍开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从窗边开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}各位初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我叫青柳一子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不是椅子 是一子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有个上高三的哥哥但不叫一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}妹妹也不叫二子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是父亲为头一次生女孩太兴奋了起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 兴趣是看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那个 我叫井口真理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}初中的时候参加了排球部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}高中也想打排球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}擅长科目是古文
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}家里是开花店的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}母亲节请一定要来光顾哦 开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}差不多就这样 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啊 我不擅长在人前讲话的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 马上就轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也在紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说我是搬家过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是之前住的城市的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那种事肯定没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么兴趣爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的东西是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行什么都想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大木双叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是的 总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉第一印象比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这世界对我来说太陌生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么继续
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么重新来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小日向光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中的时候因为过于开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大家称作闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣是呼吸器潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 名字是虎太郎 老虎的虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}最喜欢的动物是老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喜欢吃的食物是烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被打也毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能那样讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算到了高中我还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法和大家一样做好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大木双叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉号是 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 并没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这样所有人都自我介绍完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么接下来发课本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排好队按顺序每种拿一本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉附近有什么气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你头发真柔顺好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眉毛也很淡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为眉毛淡得就像两个点一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就取名小点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常可爱的绰号小点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就决定是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说一直在为我想这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去取教科书吧 小点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 叫小点有些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 小日向同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以叫我闪光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉链开着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也会害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前没见过这种孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没见过会做这种事的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净是初次见到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 于是成为高中生的各位从今天开始要自觉发奋学习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之类的大道理说实话可以放在第二位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论哭还是笑都是转瞬即逝的高中三年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样做取决于你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力学习也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽全力参与社团活动也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是疯玩也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是 在这学校里三年间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们每天都过得开开心心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心就是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心就是正义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 开心就是无限大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后的三年间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 老师刚才说出了句名言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说出了名言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里会有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请全力享受明天开始的学校生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小点你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢哪个课本的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 课本的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语文
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 语文是最好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心是无限大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说实话我不太懂
